ActCannabis Act
SubjectQualifications for Designation as Analyst Regulations (Cannabis)
PrecisQUALIFICATIONS FOR DESIGNATION AS ANALYST REGULATIONS (CANNABIS) in order to support the government’s public health and public safety goals of restricting youth access to cannabis, minimizing the harms of cannabis use, and preventing criminals and organized crime from profiting from the production of cannabis.
